  "body": "<p>Hello everyone! It’s <a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Zinia</a> here and today I want to share with you a really fun rainbow collage background I created using the new Hustle &amp; Heart collection designed by Amy.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595295114383-178NZJDWDKCCA4XJFVNL/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I was totally inspired by the paint stroke pattern paper that’s included in the collection so I decided to cut it into strips and find patterns with similar color.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>I paired each paint stroke with a subtle monochromatic pattern and then I started building up a chevron design for my background.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595295175291-L34DDNAKNAJ2ZZMGXF18/7b-Zinia-RainbowChevron-02.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Since my colors are very bright and bold the background will be pretty “heavy”. To keep everything balanced and pleasing to the eye, I kept everything else very minimal. I used a bright photo and the only embellishments I added were a few clear stickers. I made sure my stickers followed the rainbow order of the background so everything looks nice and cohesive.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595295196098-4S21KQ2OD6FKH5SXWM6F/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>To lighten things up I added some white ink splatters. I also decided to bring in a few more white elements so I picked a white foam word and a few hearts from the thickers set to add on the page.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595295220251-78C622GME87RJG5LJEQ6/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The process of creating this layout is very easy and it doesn’t take much time. The result is really nice and bright and it’s especially perfect if you enjoy creating your own unique collage backgrounds.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595295235829-J4NVEUQ6I030JCUPJBDH/7e-Zinia-RainbowChevron-05.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Zinia<br/><a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Abstract Inspiration Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abstractinspiration/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbstractInsp\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbstractInspirationPage\">Facebook</a></p><p><strong>SUPPLY LIST:</strong></p><p>341858 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Love Wins | 341862 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Hear Me Roar | 341864 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper In Alignment | 341865 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Coming Up Roses | 341868 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Oh So Lovely | 340871 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Floral Sensation | 340873 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Click Click | 340874 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper The Bright Side | 340878 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Sweet Sensation | 340880 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Take Note | 340879 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Cut It Out | 341884 Hustle &amp; Heart - STICKER BOOK | 341887 Hustle &amp; Heart - THICKERS The Lucky Ones | 378746 On a Whim - THICKERS LOL</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this colorful and creative layout, Zinia! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now on </em><em>our shop site</em><em>! </em></p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
